---
title: Christmas Ham Sandwich with sage stuffing | serves 2
description: A sandwich fit for Santa filled with ham, cranberry chutney and homemade sage stuffing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_RA_R5002_W49_IE_IEA28980-2_Main_F1_high-1b7a79bc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/66e843917dfc60d59bf5fa7e-en-IE.pdf
